on the building.

543
00:36:28,561 --> 00:36:30,271
-Is that right?
-More importantly,

544
00:36:31,230 --> 00:36:34,609
she wants to sue my mother for defamation.

545
00:36:35,568 --> 00:36:37,653
What does she mean by defamation?

546
00:36:37,737 --> 00:36:40,114
