594
00:41:13,888 --> 00:41:16,265
Have you always been this brazen?

595
00:41:20,186 --> 00:41:21,353
Get out.

596
00:41:21,437 --> 00:41:22,563
I'm working.

597
00:41:22,646 --> 00:41:24,565
After what you did to Mother,

598
00:41:24,648 --> 00:41:26,859
